                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tanazzahu-minal-bauli%e2%80%8b">
                            1. tanazzahu minal bauli​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>............................. </p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tanazzahu-minal-bauli-fainna-aamata-lanjut-kan%e2%80%8b">
                            2. tanazzahu minal bauli fainna aamata lanjut kan​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p> Adzabil qabri minhu </p><p></p><p>Artinya: Bersucilah dari air kencing, karena umumnya siksa kubur disebabkan oleh hal itu.</p><p></p><p>Hadits sahih riwayat Bukhari dan Muslim</p><p></p><p>____________________________________________</p><p></p><p><strong>O</strong><strong>H</strong><strong> </strong><strong>I</strong><strong>Y</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>,</strong><strong> </strong><strong>J</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>N</strong><strong>G</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>N</strong><strong> </strong><strong>L</strong><strong>U</strong><strong>P</strong><strong>A</strong><strong> </strong><strong>F</strong><strong>O</strong><strong>L</strong><strong>L</strong><strong>O</strong><strong>W</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Y</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>H</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>.</strong></p><p><strong>m</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>k</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>s</strong><strong>Y</strong><strong>i</strong><strong>H</strong><strong>♡</strong></p><br />
